  m_text: 'THIS IS THE BIG ONE: COLOR-A-CUBE IS OFFICIALLY 1.0!


    WE''VE ADDED
    A COLOR PALETTE AND BRUSH: A WHOLE NEW WAY TO PICK YOUR COLORS AND PAINT. MODELS
    LOOK BETTER THAN EVER NOW, WITH AMBIENT OCCLUSION GIVING THEM MORE DEPTH. THERE
    ARE ACHIEVEMENTS TO UNLOCK AS YOU GO, AND A REPLAY MODE THAT PLAYS BACK EXACTLY
    HOW YOU COLORED A MODEL, CUBE BY CUBE. YOU CAN ALSO GET A SNEAK PEEK AT THE PACKS
    AND MODELS COMING SOON.


    NONE OF THIS WOULD HAVE HAPPENED WITHOUT YOU, THANK
    YOU FOR HELPING US GET HERE. THE FULL COLOR-A-CUBE IS FINALLY HERE!'
